{"tid":345398,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"私家醫院 VS 公立醫院","createTime":"2017-08-03T05:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T11:55:00.000Z","uid":87120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4072c486f7702461ee9d89a3296fdb049b67649","tid":345398,"uid":87120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T05:05:18.000Z","msg":"好想討論下 私 / 公 既實際用途...<br />\n<br />\n曾經有個朋友，個小朋友夜晚發燒 ，<br />\n帶左佢去私家醫院，住左一晚 ，<br />\n第二日 私家醫院覺得病情嚴重 ，Pass 左佢去 政府醫院 。<br />\n<br />\n無耐政府醫生同對父母講，小朋友情況比較嚴重 ， 甲型流感個案黎 。<br />\n可能你地要有心理準備...<br />\n父母嚇到腳到軟....<br />\n好彩最後 小朋友 大步欖過... 平安出到院 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢件事...令到我覺得...<br />\n私院到底有咩用處 ？<br />\n<br />\n小病可以睇診所...<br />\n大病睇你又唔肯醫...<br />\n<br />\n之前試過同老婆去做 BodyCheck 之類...<br />\n又要預約夾岩醫生有返工果日先可以去...<br />\n一星期得 2 日可以揀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係有急事 都唔知好唔好去私家醫院 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874ee53b24d8ea5603cb13b965d89772e6dd76fd","tid":345398,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T05:08:22.000Z","msg":"私院唔係主打急症重病<br />\n<br />\n係以服務作招徠<br />\n<br />\n生仔可唔可以去診所？<br />\n<br />\n一般風險手術去私院做會照料好啲"},{"pid":"6cce197e04accf3675824c4265922d908c46114a","tid":345398,"uid":23871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"私院割下痣瘡就得 大病一定係去番公院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32525714a2cb70203c0a347c3f3cd4a354c647a","tid":345398,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8273a43ab92a8772de1f408ff74a8bc2b0c9a2c2","tid":345398,"uid":87120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"